1. Basic HTML and HTML5
  1) h1, h2, p, lorem ipsum text, <!-- -->
  2) H5 
    header, footer, nav, video, article, section
    <main>the main context of web page</main>
  3) <img src="#" alt="replace text">
      outer: <a href="#" target="_blank"></a> -- can be updated by JS by using "#" as a fixed link
      inner: <a href="#id"></a>
      embed, img embed
   4) unordered lists: <ul><li></li>..</ul>
      ordered lists: <ol><li></li>..</ol>
   5) form
      <form action="#">
        textbox: <input type="text" placeholder="a text placeholder" required>
        radio button: <label for="id"><input type="radio" name="item" id="id" checked>item1</label>
        checkboxes: <label for="id"><input type="checkbox" name="item" id="id" checked>item1</label>
        button: <button type="submit"></button>
      </form>
      
