2. Basic CSS
  1) style: external, internal, inline
  2) font-size, font-family
    import external font family: <link>
    font-family: item1, item2; // degrade use
  3)width
    border: border-color, border-style, border-width, border-radius:10px/50%
    background-color
  4) class: class="class1 class2"
     id: unique
     id>class
  5) margin, padding, border, width
     when margin is negative, the box wil fill the parent page
  6) prority
     inherit<class(ordered)<id<inline<!import
  7) color
     hex: #ffffff #fff
     rgb: rgb(255, 255, 255)
  8) CSS variable
     define: --var: value; 
     reference: var(--var, back-up value)
     root define global variable
  9) media query
     @media(condition){}
